ZH: 我们公司的网络系统安装了防火墙来保护数据信息。
EN: Our company's network system is installed with a firewall to protect data information.

ZH: 在互联网上，防火墙可以有效地阻止恶意软件和黑客攻击。
EN: On the internet, a firewall can effectively prevent malware and hacker attacks.

ZH: 请确保您的电脑上有防火墙来保护个人隐私和文件。
EN: Please make sure your computer has a firewall to protect personal privacy and files.

ZH: 虚拟专用网络与防火墙一起使用，可以增强网络安全性。
EN: Virtual Private Networks used with firewalls can enhance network security.

ZH: 大型企业通常会投资大量资金来购买和维护防火墙系统。
EN: Large enterprises often invest a substantial amount of money in purchasing and maintaining firewall systems.

ZH: 他们在公司的网络上添加了多层次的防火墙以提高安全性。
EN: They added multiple layers of firewalls on the company's network to enhance security.

ZH: 防火墙是网络安全的基础，没有它就会有严重漏洞。
EN: Firewalls are the foundation of network security, without them, there will be serious vulnerabilities.

ZH: 家庭用户可以使用防火墙软件来保护家庭网络免受恶意软件攻击。
EN: Home users can use firewall software to protect their home network from malware attacks.

ZH: 确保你的手机也有防火墙，以避免信息被窃取。
EN: Make sure your phone also has a firewall to prevent information theft.

ZH: 防火墙可以监控网络流量，识别可能的威胁并阻止它们。
EN: Firewalls can monitor network traffic, identify potential threats, and block them.

ZH: 在公共无线网络上使用VPN和防火墙是保护隐私的好方法。
EN: Using VPN and a firewall on public Wi-Fi networks is a good way to protect privacy.

ZH: 建议定期检查防火墙设置，确保它们适应最新的网络威胁。
EN: It is recommended to regularly check firewall settings to ensure they adapt to the latest network threats.

ZH: 防火墙可以过滤入侵尝试，并迅速做出响应来保护网络资源。
EN: Firewalls can filter intrusion attempts and respond quickly to protect network resources.

ZH: 所有员工必须遵守公司网络使用政策以确保防火墙的有效性。
EN: All employees must comply with the company's network usage policies to ensure the effectiveness of the firewall.

ZH: 在设计网络架构时，需考虑防火墙的放置位置以最大程度地提高安全性。
EN: When designing network architecture, consider the placement of firewalls to maximize security.

ZH: 防火墙的设置应该基于网络的特定需求和风险分析。
EN: Firewall settings should be based on specific network requirements and risk analysis.

ZH: 当网络发生异常流量时，防火墙会自动触发警报以警告管理员。
EN: When abnormal traffic occurs on the network, the firewall will automatically trigger alerts to warn administrators.

ZH: 敏感数据通常需要额外的层次的防火墙保护以确保安全。
EN: Sensitive data usually requires additional layers of firewall protection to ensure security.

ZH: 防火墙不仅仅是一种安全措施，还可以提高网络性能和可靠性。
EN: Firewalls are not just a security measure, they can also enhance network performance and reliability.
